18
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:16,680
If amplitude 12-15 Volts, then resistance 360 Ohm.

19
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:25,660
Further, modulating signal from driver HCPL3120 supplied through current-limiting resistance 47 Ohm to switch.

20
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:38,500
Switch introduced with purpose to scheme so could switch whole system to continuous work mode or work in bursts mode with modulation frequency that's at input.

21
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:47,320
Signal modulation done directly on microchip TC4093 since at its input has logic two.

22
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:56,560
That is if at each of inputs of logic element there's logical one, signal further with us passes.

23
00:02:56,680 --> 00:03:00,900
